                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>House of Lords <a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2024-01-16/debates/3A5F8F32-3503-483A-824A-4029CF3602E3/Trade(ComprehensiveAndProgressiveAgreementForTrans-PacificPartnership)Bill(HL)"><u>Vol. 835 Col. 321</u></a></p>
                </td>
