            <p eId="annex_2_p_9"><b>Annex B - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>66 </num>
              <p>The Trade (Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership) Act extends to the whole of the UK except for section 3(4)(a) and Part 1 (amendments to procurement regulations for England and Wales and Northern Ireland) and section 3(4)(b) and Part 2 of the Schedule (amendments to procurement regulations for Scotland). </p>
            </blockContainer>
            <p>The information provided is the view of the UK Government.</p>
            <table uk:widths="0.73in 1.28in 1.48in 1.48in 1.81in">
